\id GLO - Kein NT [bmh] -Papua New Guinea 2005 (DBL -2014) 
\h Ze bigeg ipal abiu mabun 
\toc2 Ze bigeg ipal abiu mabun 
\toc1 Ze bigeg ipal abiu mabun 
\mt1 Ze bigeg ipal abiu mabun  
\li1 \k Babilon \k*  
\li2 Asiria emgasag goagal ban uzan. Getal Asiria goagal malai dudu agen Israel duailel imaraimai, Babilon ban uzan betei hiacaranem zau oug hiacaremen.  
\li2 Agau Araogan Ze ebu, uzan go duailel goagal igul eg pet daremen gonugau wanib Babilon anem. Uwait nug uzan go unum egwai meun.  
\li1 \k Baib bogis \k*  
\li2 \it Bogis \it* go Israel duailel agen usalai maimai, em ula ebu wageimai aidanemen. Go Uwait go abai dareu abai maraneun. Kasai ze houhou go aiwag aliag ebu Uwait nug Moses moroun, baib \it bogis \it* go oug memenin (\xt Hibru 9:1-5\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Balam \k*  
\li2 Du go gue Uwait nugau ze doimai, awaraneu du. Go aiwag wabun ougab alina, Uwait nugau ze sesamorabun utena, gonugau egun \it donki \it* go kagagai aureun. (\xt Namba 22:1-35\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Barak \k*  
\li2 Barak go Israel duailel goagal gumaraneun du tub. (\xt Hetman 4:6\xt* noi betei 5:15 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Enimag galau kuatabun igul \k*  
\li2 Go Zuda dudu agal igul, geleagar gil 8 mazicina, goagal enimag galau kuataranem. Go igul go en, Israel duailel Uwait dual baib memen abai maranem.  
\li1 \k Enok \k*  
\li2 Du go gue Adam nugau ug ebuan. (\xt Stat 5:18-24\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Gagaliag patanemen igul \k*  
\li2 Igul go ze ziwarabun igul sul. Duailel Yesus en oiagab petak emen, duailel ipal agen abe marabun \it sios \it* ipal go igul sesamoraimai, guzenanem.  
\li1 \k Gideon \k*  
\li2 Gideon go Israel duailel goagal gumaraneun du tub. (Hetman 6:1 noi betei 8:35 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Gol \k*  
\li2 Ece go \it ain \it* sul, baila. Dudu agen em ougan tulai wanemen. Amegai go em ai mui gotulai dacaneu. Ab zabeg nug agena, \it gol \it* ze sul usalaimai, nuna, dudu agen gotulai macanemen. Ece \it gol \it* eiman patai memen gau mabun, na aiwag asiu asiu himam.  
\li1 \k Hagar \k*  
\li2 Go Abraham wau nugau salau air. (\xt Stat 16:1-16\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Herodias \k*  
\li2 Air go Herot nugau amag, Pilip gonugau wau. (\xt Matiu 14:1-12\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Herot \k*  
\li2 Dudu aliag wanimag guzenai mui. Du tub, go Herot Banou anemen. Go Uwait nugan Nou zau tub meun. Aiu ses, go mogoi ginaginam asiu ugarina, noumemen. (Matiu 2 na pen.)  
\li2 Herot tub go wanib tub Antipas. (\xt Matiu 14:1-12; Luk 23:7\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Israel \k*  
\li2 Getal Aisak nugau nag, Zekop gonugau wanib awau Israel oun. (Stat 32:28 na pen.)  
\li2 Aiu ses gonugau ug Kenan emgasag betei omenin. Gonugau embigeg ig Israel duailel anem, ziwas ipal ebu go Zuda duailel anem.  
\li1 \k Kasai ze tapaimaranem dudu \k*  
\li2 Dudu go agen Zuda agal kasai ze tapaimaranemen. Go Moses nugau kasai ze mui kasai ze ipal asiu go dudu agtal usalaraimai tapaimaranemen. Goagal kasai ze asiu 613 zilacoroun. Goagen duailel kasai ze go unum sesamorabun en gusig awaranemen. Dudu goagen Yesus dual ze alalanemen.  
\li1 \k Kora \k*  
\li2 Israel duailel go em ula ebu aidaremen ziwas ebu, du go nug Moses dual ze alalaimai, go dual iwai dareun. (\xt Namba 16:1-35\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Kristus \k*  
\li2 Wanib gonugau zebigeg enai: Uwait nug duailel agal igul eg ebuan koli imarabun tapai moroun du. Ig Kristen duailel abiu, du go gue Yesus tutak. Kristus go Grik ze eim, Hibru ze eim Mesaia anem.  
\li1 \k Liwai \k*  
\li2 Dudu aliag wanimag guzenai mui. Du tub, go Yesus nugau ze oi aidaneun du, wanib tub Matiu.  
\li2 Liwai tub go Zekop nugau nag tub. Uwait nug dudu ipal Liwai nugau ug ebuan, Uwait ula dabun dudu tapai mareun, ipal go Nou Zaueim salau isanarabun tapai mareun.  
\li1 \k Maikel \k*  
\li2 Go Uwait nugau tibur gumaraneu tibur banou. (\xt Daniel 12:1\xt* na pen.)  
\li2 Zuda agal ze tub ebu, Moses noumeun ziwas ebu, Satan nug Moses nugau enib noumeun oi unai aimai aneun. Moses nugau enib noumeun oi unabun go Maikel nugau salau, gonun, Maikel go abiu go iboin tam, bo, go Satan dual ze i alaleu. Go soai darena, Uwait nugtal Satan ze aureun, “Na guzen i en.”  
\li1 \k Mana \k*  
\li2 Ee go atai. Getal Israel duailel Izip emgasag uteimai, em ula ebu Uwait nug ee go wanib mana marena, zemenin. Ee go ausiau, kel naliupet. Wanib go Hibru ze eim gonugau zebigeg “E ein?”. (\xt Kisim Bek 16:1-36; Namba\xt* 11:4-9 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Melkisedek \k*  
\li2 Go Uwait wag dareu nugau ula dacaneu du. Abraham go betei dudu banban iwanarai abai malai maimai, koli alaimai abu ebu, Melkisedek tuloroun. (\xt Stat 14:17-20\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Onesimus \k*  
\li2 Du go getal \it slev \it* dareun, bo, aiu ses gonugau ougab ailaimai, go Pol dual Rom uzan daremen. (\xt Pilemon 10; Kolosi 4:9\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Parisi dudu \k*  
\li2 Zuda dudu go Yesus nugau ziwas ebu daremen. Dudu go Moses nugau kasai ze mui goagal kasai ze ipal Uwait nugau ameg ebu naliu dabun gusig sesamoranemenin. Pol go Parisi du. Dudu goagen Yesus dual ze alalanemen.  
\li1 \k Pilip \k*  
\li2 Dudu ainarai wanimag guzenai mui. Du tub, go Yesus nugau ze oi aidaneun du. (\xt Matiu 10:3\xt* na pen.)  
\li2 Pilip tub go Zerusalem oiagab petak emen duailel agal isanaraneun du. (Aposel 6:5, 8:26-40 na pen.)  
\li2 Pilip tub go Herot nugau amag. (\xt Mak 6:17-18\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Rama \k*  
\li2 Uzan tub Betlehem waugab dareun. Go Samuel nugau uzan. Getal uzan go wanib banou mui dacaneun. Gonun, duailel Rama anem, go Zuda duailel unum en dabilanem.  
\li1 \k Sadiusi dudu \k*  
\li2 Go Zuda dudu ipal, Yesus nugau ziwas ebu daremen. Dudu go enanem, duair noumaimai, koli asamam en agal oiagab petak i emenin. Go enanem, Uwait nugau tibur mui tibur ipal mui i darem anem. Dudu go agen Yesus dual ze alalanemen.  
\li1 \k Saion \k*  
\li2 Go em tabag. Go ebu, Zerusalem ban uzan dareu. Duailel ipal goagen Saion go Zerusalem anem. Agau Araogan Ze ebu, Saion go Zerusalem awau Mesgai wag dareu.  
\li1 \k Salpa \k*  
\li2 Aiwag go baila. Ab elaneu em tabag pou aimai, aiwag \it salpa \it* go alaneu. Aiwag go koli ab ebu mina, zabeg banou pet macaneu.  
\li1 \k Samaria duailel \k*  
\li2 Duailel go Samaria agaig an, go Uwait ulagwag muranemen. Bo, goagal dabeleu go Uwait nug Zerusalem go i dareu, getal goagal Uwait ecesab muranemen zau em tabag Kerisim ebu memenin, Bo, iwai zaiagar agen zau go eg wai memenin. Goagal dabeleu go em tabag Kerisim ebu Uwait ulagwag murabun iboin. (\xt Zon 4:21\xt* na pen.)  
\li2 Zuda duailel agal dabeleu go Samaria duailel unu mui, gonun, go abai i gotulanemen.  
\li1 \k Samson \k*  
\li2 Samson go Israel duailel goagal gumaraneun du tub. Go du gusigwa pet. (\xt Hetman 13:24\xt* noi betei 16:30 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Samuel \k*  
\li2 Samuel go Uwait nugau ze doimai, awaraneun du tub. Go King Devit nugau ziwas ebu dacaneun. (1 Samuel na pen.)  
\li1 \k Sekaraia \k*  
\li2 Dudu aliag wanimag guzenai mui. Du tub, go ze ziwaraneun du, Zon nugau memeg. (\xt Luk 1:5-67\xt* na pen.)  
\li2 Sekaraia tub go Uwait nugau ze doimai, awaraneun du. Dudu ipal agen wina, noumeun. \it Olpela Testamen \it* ebu, dudu ipal agen dudu asiu wagarina, noumemenin. Go ebuan, Sekaraia nugau ze ulis sikut wemen dareu. (\xt 2 Stori 24:20-21\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Silva \k*  
\li2 Ece go \it gol \it* sul, go ausiau.  
\li1 \k Sisar \k*  
\li2 Du go gue Rom emgasag gumaraneun du banou King sul.  
\li1 \bdit Slev\bdit*  
\li2 Duailel go goagal atag du nugau pigsal dacanemen. Goagal salau utei unabun iborain tam. Atag du naliu go suban gumaraneun, bo, atag du egonou go uhu asiu maraneun. Goagal atag dudu agal ameagab ebu go egun sul. Dudu ipal agen go gau marabun iboin.  
\li2 \it Slev \it* ipal go aiwag ginampet oimai, tulaimai, banou usalina, go agtal goagal aiwag atag du muranem, Guzenaimai, go ziwas ebu, go \it slev \it* i damau.  
\li1 \k Tatau ze \k*  
\li2 Ze tuguiai wageimai darena, duailel gaul tatau ze eiman ze macanemen. Yesus nug duailel tatau ze eiman awaraneun.  
\li1 \k Uwait ecesab muranemen zau banou \k*\it (Tempel) \it*  
\li2 Zau go Zerusalem ban uzan tutak dareu Ziwas ipal ig Nou Zau anem. (Zuda duailel Uwait ulagwag murabun goagal gotulanemen zau ginaginam goagal uzan beu beu dareu.) Uwait ula dacanemen dudu agen zau banou go gumanemen. Duailel unum ein zobu ziwas banou dabelabun zaueim go Uwait nugau wanib ulagwag muranemen.  
\li2 Amegai Solomon nug zau banou go Zerusalem uzan meun. Dai dai, iwai zaiagar agen zau go eg wai mina, Esra zaug Nehemia dual agen zau tub memenin. Dai dai, zau go eg wina, \it king \it* Herot nug koli meun. Yesus noumeun wai 40 mazicina, zobu zau banou go Rom agal malai dudu agen unum eg wai memenin. Ulis, i dareu.  
\li1 \k Uwait nugau tibur \k*\it (ensel) \it*  
\li2 Tibur go agen Uwait nugau ze oi aidaimai, gonugau salau muranemen.  
\li1 \k Uwait nugau ze doimai, awaranemen duailel \k*\it (profet) \it*  
\li2 Duailel go Uwait nugtal gonugau ogusau ebuan ze doimai, gonugau duailel awarabun tapai mareun. Duailel ipal guzeneneg goagal wanimag: Aisaia, Zeremaia, Elaiza, Samuel, Miriam, Ana.  
\li1 \k Uwait ula dacanemen dudu \k*\it (pris) \it*  
\li2 Uwait nug dudu go gonugau duailel go dual ula dabun en tapai mareun. Go Liwai nugau ug ebuan. Go Uwait nugau Nou Zau banou gumeimai, Uwait nugau biz ebu egun agaimai, duailel agal pip oimai, Uwait ecesab moroimai, go duailel en Uwait auranemen Yesus nugau ziwas ebu, dudu go agen Yesus dual ze alalanem.  
\li1 \k Uwait ula dacanemen dudu banban \k*\it (bik pris) \it*  
\li2 Dudu go Uwait ula dacanemen dudu ipal gumaranem dudu banban.  
\li1 \k Uwait ula dacaneu du banou pet \k*\it (Het pris) \it*  
\li2 Uwait ula dacanemen dudu agen du go goagal gumarabun du banou tapai moromen. Wai tutak tutak, gil tutak ebu gonug sag duailel agal pip oimai, Uwait nugau ameg ebu zau empip nou pet oug simai, duailel agal igul eg macanemen zilagai marabun guzenaneun. Ulis, Yesus nug gonugau eseu sil igual igul eg zilagai migeun, gonun, go tutak go igual Uwait ula dacaneu du banou pet.  
\li1 \k Yesus nugau tapaimaraneu dudu \k*\it (disaipel) \it*  
\li2 Dudu go Yesus sesamorina, gonug gonugau igul tapaimaraneun.  
\li1 \k Yesus nugau ze oi aidanemen dudu \k* \it (aposel) \it*  
\li2 Gonugau tapaimaraneu dudu go ulacan Yesus nug dudu begurug gonugau ze oi aidabun aimai tapai mareun. Goagen gonugau abai maraneun ze oimai, duailel ipal abai maranemen. (\xt Mak 3:13-19\xt* na pen.)  
\li2 Dudu ipal han wanimag guzenai mui, Pol, Barnabas. (\xt Aposel 14:14\xt* na pen.)  
\li1 \k Zanes zaug Zampres dual \k*  
\li2 Go Izip emgasag agal gumaraneu du banou, Pero nugau oz ze abiu dudu aliag. (\xt Kisim Bek 7:22\xt* noi betei 9:11 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Zau empip nou \k*  
\li2 Go Uwait ecesab muranemen zaueim zau empip nou. Empip go ebu Uwait ula dacanemen dudu tutak tutak simai, salau macanemen. Dudu gaul gaul zau empip go oug siabun iborain tam.  
\li1 \k Zau empip nou pet \k*  
\li2 Zau empip nou pet, zau empip nou go \it laplap \it* banou sil tapelai memenin seugab dareu. Baib bogis go zau empip nou pet go oug memenin dareun. Empip nou pet go Uwait nug dacaneun. Gonun, du tub empip go oug siabun iborain tam. Wai tutak tutak, gil tutak ebu Uwait ula dacaneu du banou pet gonug sag igul eg zilagabun zau empip go oug siabun iboin.  
\li1 \k Ze ziwabun igul \k*  
\li2 Getal Zuda duailel go agal igul eg ebuan ailemen abai marabun, dudu ipal go ze unig oug suaraimai, koli imaranem. Ulis duailel Yesus en oiagab petak emen, duailel ipal agen abe marabun go igul sul guzenanemen. Guzenaimai, ag abiu duailel goagal getalan igul uteimai, duailel awau usalanem. Gagaliag patanemen igul go sul.  
\li1 \k Zepta \k*  
\li2 Zepta go Israel duailel goagal gumaraneun du tub. (\xt Hetman 11:1\xt* noi betei 12:7 na pen.)  
\li1 \k Zeremaia \k*  
\li2 Zeremaia go Uwait nugau ze doimai, awaraneun du tub. Israel duailel gonugau ze duabun uteimai, go uhu asiu moromenin.  
\li1 \k Zuda \k*  
\li2 Zuda go Zekop nugau nag tub.  
\li2 Getal King Solomon go Israel emgasag gumaneun. Go noumina, gonugau nag nug gonugau empip oun. Ziwas go ebu, Israel go atalaimai, ipal wanimag Israel duailel daremen, ipal wanimag Zuda duailel usalemenin. Zuda nugau ug eiman betei Yesus usaleun.  
\li1 \k 1. Balau uanem zobu \k*  
\li2 Zobu go Zuda agal wai bigegwabun balau uanem. Go balau doimai, i maimai, iauiau dacanemen. Zobu go Oktoba 1 waugab.  
\li1 \k 2. Igul eg zilagaimai, Uwait dual oiagab tutak mai dabun gil. \k*  
\li2 Gil go ebu, Uwait ula dacaneu du banou pet go tutak, gonug Uwait nugau zau empip nou pet, \it laplap \it* banou sil abu tapelai memen go oug egun eseu oi simai, duailel agal igul eg zilagai marabun gorianeu. Uwait nug duailel go waugab imarai bitabun aimai guzenaneu. Gil go ebu, Zuda duailel go salau i macanemen. Zobu go Balau uanem Zobu sesamoraneu.  
\li1 \k 3. Ougem zau dabun zobu \k*  
\li2 Zobu ziwas go ebu, Zuda duailel go wit unum oimai, Uwait ‘Ese-e’ aurabun goagal ougem zau maimai, dacanemen. Zobu go getal Zuda duailel Izip emgasag uteimai, em ula ebu salap zau gabuai alemen dabeleimai, guzenanemen. Zobu go Oktoba 15-21 ula.  
\li1 \k 4. Nou zau im oitemen ziwas. \k*  
\li2 Ziwas go ebu, getal Zuda duailel go malalai ziwas siksikanemenin. Bo, dai dai, dudu ipal agen Zerusalem Nou Zau eg wai mina, du tub wanib Zudas-Makabius nug wai tub gil go ebu, Uwait nugau zau eg wai memen suban maimai, im oiteun, gonun, ulis gil go ebu duailel gonugau igul en dabilanemen. Gil go ebu, duailel al asiu macanemen, gonun, go Al Zobu amen. Zobu go Desemba10-17 ula.  
\li1 \k 5. Pasowa \k*  
\li2 Go Zuda agal zobu tub, getal agal embigeg Izip emgasag darena, hiacaranem salau maimai, wai 400 daremen. Ziwas go ebu, Uwait nug Israel duailel sipsip nag waimai, gonugau eseu oimai, goagal zau og gasageim zau sanag ebu ziorabun eun, gonun, gonugau tibur agen goagal zau etuboroimai, betei, Izip agal geleagar kaman wagarina, noumemenin. Gonun, Israel duailel ulis Uwait nug go suban gumareun en dabilanemen.  
\li2 Yesus Pasowa ziwas tub ebu, wina noumeun. Ziwas go Ista waugab.  
\li1 \k 6. Bret zis tamacag zabun zobu. \k*  
\li2 Zobu go getal Israel duailel go Izip emgasag utei alemen ziwas ebu \it bret \it* zis tamacag zemenin dabeleimai, Zobu go ebu \it bret \it* zis tamacag zanem. Zobu go Pasowa ziwas sesamoraneu.  
\li1 \k 7. Pentikos \k*  
\li2 Zobu go Zuda duailel agal ee awau ougem an oimai, Uwait muranemen. Zobu go, gil kwali go ebu Uwait ulagwag muranemen.  
\li2 Yesus noumina, Pentikos gil tub ebu, emgasag ebuan duailel unum alai, Zerusalem ban uzan Uwait ulagwag murabun gotulanemen. Ziwas go ebu guzenina guzenina, Uwait nugau Ah Wes aleun. Gonun, ig ulis Pentikos gil ebu Ah Wes en dabilanem. Ista zuaneun, gil 50 mazicina, Zobu go zuaneu.  